<br />
3. In the mean time I suggest that we form an effective Working Party of all the SESA ex presidents and the current one to work on this, i.e., look at the best options for a way forward, use the Newsletter/Forum to communicate options and eventually promote the best one for consideration via an inclusive postal (or e-postal) referendum. The Extraordinary AGM will then be the ratification vehicle for the option accepted by the majority. <br />
